Thank you for registering for Skloop!<br />
When you click finish registration will redirect you to Twitter to login, and verify Skloop as a trustworthy application.
<% form_for @user, :url => {:action => 'update'} do |f| %>
<%= hidden_field_tag :direction, "register" %>
<%= label_tag :username, "Username:" %><br />
<%= f.text_field :username %>
<%= submit_tag "Finish" %>
<% end %>
